title: BRIEF-Nordic Semiconductor wins new $1.7 million order
text:
BRIEF-Nordic Semiconductor wins new $1.7 million order 
Oct 16 Nordic Semiconductor ASA : 
* Has received a new order for components to Wearables Market for a total value of $1.7 million 
* Delivery of components will take place in Q4 2015 and Q1 2016 Source text for Eikon:
